HEADWORD: Helminthite
<hw>Hel*min"thite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/, <?/, a
worm.]</ety> <fld>(Geol.)</fld> <def>One of the sinuous tracks on the
